nov.se\" href=\"mailto:malin.fredriksson@mannov.se\">malin.fredriksson@mannov.se</a>. Julia sterlund (AGRIA / Agrias Ponnyklubb): <a title=\"mailto:julia.osterlund@agria.se\" href=\"mailto:julia.osterlund@agria.se\">julia.osterlund@agria.se </a>Ange namn p <span class=\"style\">ryttare och ponnyer, plats och datum</span>.</p>\\r\\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_9\">Varmt vlkomna till trningsserien SUGAR CUP! Pernilla och Ted</p>\\r\\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"211\" img_size=\"large\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]<a href=\"http://localhost/flyingehus_new/sugar-cup-skane/\"><img class=\"img-link\" src=\"http://localhost/flyingehus_new/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/sugarcup_skane.png\" /> </a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]<a href=\"http://localhost/flyingehus_new/sugar-cup/pressrum/\"><img class=\"img-link\" src=\"http://localhost/flyingehus_new/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/sugarcup_pressrum.png\" /> </a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]<a href=\"http://localhost/flyingehus_new/sugar-cup/fakta/\"><img class=\"img-link\" src=\"http://localhost/flyingehus_new/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/fakta_sugar.png\" /> </a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row disable_element=\"yes\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_tta_accordion gap=\"5\" active_section=\"non-existing\" title=\"REGIONER, KONTAKTER, TIDSPLAN\"][vc_tta_section title=\"SUGAR CUP SKNE\" tab_id=\"1476445867456-28958c2b-cc59\"][vc_column_text]\\r\\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_7\">Omgng 1: Flyinge 5 maj Omgng 2: Dagstorp 12 juni Omgng 3: Tgarp 26 juni</p>\\r\\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_5\">Kontakt: Pernilla Linder Velander  <a class=\"Ingen\" title=\"mailto:pernilla@flyingehus.com\" href=\"mailto:pernilla@flyingehus.com\">pernilla@flyingehus.com</a