 height=\"36px\"][vc_gmaps link=\"#E-8_\" size=\"400\" title=\"Hitta Hit!\"][vc_btn title=\"BOKA HR\" style=\"3d\" color=\"mulled-wine\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%3A8888%2Fflyingehus%2Fvandrarhem%2Fboka-2%2F|||\" button_block=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"379\" img_size=\"large\" onclick=\"link_image\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"382\" img_size=\"large\" onclick=\"link_image\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"380\" img_size=\"large\" onclick=\"link_image\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"381\" img_size=\"large\" onclick=\"link_image\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css=\".vc_custom_1476352631638{background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\\r\\n<h2><strong><u class=\"\">SOMMARBOX P FLYINGE</u></strong></h2>\\r\\nUnder sommaren 2016 gr det att boka box i Flyinges permanenta stallar  fr enstaka vernattning, fr kurser och trning eller vid tvling.\\r\\n\\r\\nVi disponerar boxar bl a i Stostallet, i Krstallet och i Wallenbergstallet, enligt ett rullande schema.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>INFORMATION</strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nTv balar spn ingr i bokningen den frsta natten. Extra spn finns att kpa efter behov. Grovfoder och kraftfoder tar du sjlv med till din hst.\\r\\n\\r\\nBoxen lmnas helt utmockad, senast kl 12 avresedagen. Boxen kan betalas via bankgiro vid bokningen eller med Swish/kontant p plats p Flyinge, efter verenskommelse.\\r\\n\\r\\nHsttransporter kan parkeras p anvisad plats.\\r\\n\\r\\n<em>Hstar som kommer till Flyinge ska vara vaccinerade enligt tvlingskrav. Pass/vaccinationsintyg ska kunna visas.</em>\\r\\n<em>Ofullstndigt utmockad box debiteras med 500 kr</em>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Vlkomna att boka sommarbox!</strong>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\\r\\n<h4><strong>PRISER 2017</strong></h4>\\r\\n<strong>Sommarbox p Flyinge</strong>\\r\\n<em>Uppstallning enstaka natt eller flera ntter.</em>Box, frsta natten, inkl 2 balar spn, 375 kr.\\r\\nBox, fljande ntter, 250 kr/natt.\\r\\nExtra spn, 100 kr/bal.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_empty_space height=\"36px\"][vc_gmaps link=\"#E-8_\" size=\"400\" title=\"Hitta Hit!\"][vc_btn title=\"BOKA HR\" style=\"3d\" color=\"mulled-wine\" size=\"lg\" align=\"center\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%3A8888%2Fflyingehus%2Fvandrarhem%2Fboka-2%2F|||\" button_block=\"true\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"383\" img_size=\"large\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"384\" img_size=\"large\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"385\" img_size=\"large\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"388\" img_size=\"large\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"387\" img_size=\"large\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"386\" img_size=\"large\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'VANDRARHEM', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '72-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-03 14:40:23', '2017-03-03 13:40:23', '', 72, 'http://localhost:8888/flyingehus/2017/03/03/72-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
